{"id":6861,"date":"2019-11-09T14:46:40","date_gmt":"2019-11-09T09:16:40","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/?p=6861"},"modified":"2021-09-27T18:43:54","modified_gmt":"2021-09-27T13:13:54","slug":"magento-tools-build-robust-ecommerce-website","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/magento-tools-build-robust-ecommerce-website.html","title":{"rendered":"Best Magento Development Tools to Build Robust eCommerce Website"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-6864\" src=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/magento-development-tools.jpg\" alt=\"magento development tools\" width=\"908\" height=\"441\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/magento-development-tools.jpg 908w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/magento-development-tools-300x146.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/magento-development-tools-768x373.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/magento-development-tools-600x291.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 908px) 100vw, 908px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>Magento is one of the leading open-source eCommerce platform written in PHP and one of the most popular eCommerce platforms. Created with the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/zend-framework-development.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Zend Framework<\/a>, Magento source code is distributed under an Open Source Initiative (OSI) approved by the Open Software License (OSL).<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/magento-development.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Magento development services<\/a> are fast becoming one of the popular choices for building eCommerce websites. But while the installation is simple, actually managing a store can be tough. As your store continues to grow, you&#8217;re likely to complicated requirements to run your ecommerce store efficiently, and there&#8217;ll be a need to automate as much of the process as possible. It is one of the most popular open e-commerce systems in the network.<\/p>\n<p>This list includes both free Magento and premium tools that must be purchased. Be it a small business or enterprise-level eCommerce store for a large client; these third-party tools can dramatically help to improve management, as well as provide developers the agility needed to keep the store running efficiently.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Here is the list of Magento tools with top quality standards which are easy to set up and run.<\/strong><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Debugging_and_Development_Tools\"><\/span>Debugging and Development Tools<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">\n<li><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.magentocommerce.com\/magento-connect\/commerce-bug-2.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\">Commerce Bug<\/a>:<\/strong><br \/>\nCommerce Bug 3 is the eagerly awaited upgrade to Pulse Storm&#8217;s Magento debugging extension. Commerce Bug 3 brings six years of Magento development and debugging experience to the Magento 2 platform.<\/p>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">\n<li>New dependency-injection\/object-manager features and GUI based logging for ajax and API requests.<\/li>\n<li>Legacy support for Magento 1.x and will be supported through Magento 1&#8217;s end-of-life period.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.magentocommerce.com\/magento-connect\/magneto-debug.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\">Magento Debug<\/a>:<\/strong>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">\n<li>Toggle Magento modules on and off.<\/li>\n<li>Display RAM usage as well as identify the areas of bottlenecks.<\/li>\n<li>Quickly clear the cache and toggle template hints on and off.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/EcomDev\/EcomDev_PHPUnit\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\">EcomDev PHPUnit<\/a>:<\/strong><br \/>\nThis Magento extension lets you integrate the PHPUnit framework for rapid tests of modules, models, blocks, helpers, controller actions, and layout rendering processes.<\/p>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">\n<li>Resolve the problem and promote test-driven development practices in the Magento developers community.<\/li>\n<li>Change core files or brake Magento installment database as all-system objects are replaced during the run-time with the test ones and a database connection is used for tests.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.magentocommerce.com\/magento-connect\/easy-template-path-hints.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\">Easy Template Path Hints<\/a>:<\/strong>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">\n<li>Turn on template path hints in both frontend and backend.<\/li>\n<li>It is activated by inserting a query string to any URL.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Magento_Migration_and_Version_Checking_Tools\"><\/span>Magento Migration and Version Checking Tools<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">\n<li><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/chrome.google.com\/webstore\/detail\/version-check-for-magento\/aekpbnbbbgocohlbdpdfgghamedmplal?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\">Version Check for Magento<\/a>:<\/strong>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">\n<li>A tool which allows checking the version of Magento empowering a web page.<\/li>\n<li>Version Check for Magento determines if Magento powers web pages, what version is running, and indicates if the version in use is outdated.<\/li>\n<li>The extension does not detect the version on websites running Magento Enterprise Edition.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/chrome.google.com\/webstore\/detail\/up-to-date\/gfdibfaafmpljichhkbgbegfoinihnab?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\">Up to Date?<\/a> :<\/strong>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">\n<li>Track the software versions running on various websites.<\/li>\n<li>Chrome extension provides robust support to the Community Edition plus other software.<\/li>\n<li>Allows keeping track of the version status of the web applications powering the websites you manage.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li><strong>Cloud Backup:<\/strong>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">\n<li>Get back up of data stored and archive it remotely in the cloud.<\/li>\n<li>Cloud Backup allows excluding database tables, files, and directories.<\/li>\n<li>Schedule a Cron job to fire the backup automatically.<\/li>\n<li>Compatible with Amazon S3, Google Drive, Dropbox, and Box.net.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.magentocommerce.com\/magento-connect\/moving-tool-2-0-for-magento.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\">Moving Tool 2.0<\/a>:<\/strong>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">\n<li>Quickly migrate an existing Magento store.<\/li>\n<li>The extension generates an Installer package to perform a near-instant move from server to server.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li><strong>CMS and Configuration Migrator :<\/strong>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">\n<li>An easy and efficient way to migrate data from the development environment to live.<\/li>\n<li>Extension compiles a list of changes and lets you select which ones to push to your live site.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Magento_2_Extension_for_User_Experience\"><\/span><strong>Magento 2 Extension for User Experience<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">\n<li><strong>AJAX Cart Pro for Magento 2:<\/strong><br \/>\nStreamline add-to-cart function and remove interruptions from the shopping process<\/p>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">\n<li>Select product options without visiting the product page.<\/li>\n<li>Short description, rating and reviews available right from the pop-up.<\/li>\n<li>Mobile friendly add-to-cart design depending on a screen type.<\/li>\n<li>Works on product types including bundle, grouped, and configurable products.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li><strong>Cart to Quote for Magento 2:<\/strong><br \/>\nNegotiate quotations with the customers you trust for the best win-to-win deals. Essential B2B solution!<\/p>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">\n<li>Multiple products per quote.<\/li>\n<li>Adding products to an unlocked quote from various pages.<\/li>\n<li>Alternating cession of control over the quote.<\/li>\n<li>Quote expiration reminder.<\/li>\n<li>RFQ restriction for selected customer groups.<\/li>\n<li>Various quotation statuses.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li><strong>Bambora APAC Payment for Magento 2:<\/strong><br \/>\nGet safe and fast payments, several methods enabled, with enhanced Bambora checkout, (Asia-Pacific region only).<\/p>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">\n<li>Improved security issues and usability.<\/li>\n<li>Compliance fully with PCI Security Standards, as well as compatible with the latest Magento 2 versions.<br \/>\nUse the previously saved credit card information.<\/li>\n<li>Advanced Subscription Products for Magento 2.<br \/>\nNo billing data is stored on Magento servers, only on Bambora.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Magento_Catalog_Management_Tools\"><\/span>Magento Catalog Management Tools<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">\n<li><strong>Bulk Image Uploader:<\/strong>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">\n<li>Quickly assign to the right products in your Magento store, import images in bulk, providing the images with the SKU in the file name.<\/li>\n<li>The plugin can be uploaded from your computer or a Dropbox folder.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li><strong>Age Verification:<\/strong>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">\n<li>Confirms customer date of birth before adding certain products to their cart.<\/li>\n<li>Administrators can customize and validate the age threshold and use age restrictions to individual products or entire categories. Age data is saved for future reference.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.magentocommerce.com\/magento-connect\/image-optimizer.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\">Image Optimizer<\/a>:<\/strong>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">\n<li>Compress images on-demand or via Cron for quick loading of site.<\/li>\n<li>Compatible with gif, jpg, and png files.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.magentocommerce.com\/magento-connect\/ajax-mass-image-uploader-by-iksanika.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\">Mass Image Uploader<\/a>:<\/strong>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">\n<li>Easily drag and drop images effortlessly into the product grid or remove multiple images instantly.<\/li>\n<li>Extension lets to filter the grid and apply updates in bulk.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li><strong>Social Media Product Update<\/strong>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">\n<li>Automatically make push product announcements to your social media channels.<\/li>\n<li>Send social media updates regarding new products, or inform people about promotions.<br \/>\nUse Buffer to send updates to Twitter, Facebook, Google+, LinkedIn, and other compatible social networks.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Magento_Order_and_Shipping_Management_Tools\"><\/span><strong>Magento Order and Shipping Management Tools<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">\n<li><strong>Maximum Order Amount :<\/strong>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">\n<li>Extension to avoid customers placing extremely large orders on credit when they purchase via COD or invoice payment.<\/li>\n<li>The credit limit can be set globally or for customers individually.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/ecommerce.aheadworks.com\/magento-extensions\/order-tags.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\">Order Tags<\/a>:<\/strong>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">\n<li>Tag your orders and filter according to assigned labels.<\/li>\n<li>Tags can be calculated manually or automated based on specific rules.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li><strong>Backorder Status:<\/strong>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">\n<li>This tool is extensible, increasing the default backorder behavior in Magento.<\/li>\n<li>Indicates back-ordered items and allocates stock when a delivery comes in.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li><strong>Multishipping :<\/strong>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">\n<li>Improve Magento&#8217;s native multi shipping feature with additional capabilities.<\/li>\n<li>Split an order with one click and place all shipments on hold until a pre-selected date.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li><strong>Smart Grid Actions :<\/strong>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">\n<li>Augment the default grid view with additional actions to quickly marking items as paid, managing prices, and tagging orders as shipped.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li><strong>Package List PDF :<\/strong>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">\n<li>Package list PDF can dispatch the warehouse to collect the items needed for an order.<\/li>\n<li>It is based on the order and not the shipment. The document can be printed before the shipment is made.<\/li>\n<li>The content of the package list is configurable through the backend and allows you to add a PDF as a background image.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/ecommerce.aheadworks.com\/magento-extensions\/multi-warehouse-management.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\">Multi-Warehouse Management<\/a>:<\/strong>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">\n<li>Calculate the correct shipping cost of products stored in multiple locations.<\/li>\n<li>Automatically split the order according to the area of various products.<\/li>\n<li>Introduces warehouse management.<\/li>\n<li>Allows assigning products to warehouses and mention a default warehouse to unassigned products.<\/li>\n<li>Based on item location, automatically calculates shipping.<\/li>\n<li>Splits products into several shipments.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4 style=\"font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 42px; color: #0a57f4;\">Finally<\/h4>\n<p>We hope you found this list of top Magento development tools helpful. Do let us know if you would like us to update this list with your favorite tool.<\/p>\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_47_1 ez-toc-wrap-left counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-transparent ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">Table of Contents<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/magento-tools-build-robust-ecommerce-website.html\/#Debugging_and_Development_Tools\" title=\"Debugging and Development Tools\">Debugging and Development Tools<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/magento-tools-build-robust-ecommerce-website.html\/#Magento_Migration_and_Version_Checking_Tools\" title=\"Magento Migration and Version Checking Tools\">Magento Migration and Version Checking Tools<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/magento-tools-build-robust-ecommerce-website.html\/#Magento_2_Extension_for_User_Experience\" title=\"Magento 2 Extension for User Experience\">Magento 2 Extension 